Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.62,0:01:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起加入裤头村最崇高最勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We join Bikini Bottom's noblest, boldest
