Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But wait
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.59,0:01:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的英雄到度假村放松期间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While our heroes relax at Leisure Village
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.52,0:01:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁来帮美人鱼基地看家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who will watch the Mermalair?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵战士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ManSponge
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.00,0:01:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,和海星男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And BoyPatrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.35,0:01:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reporting for duty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.02,0:01:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up, up and away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们想要你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, we want you boys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.73,0:01:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to keep an eye on the place
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮绿植浇水  并且确保
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water the plants and make sure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.84,0:01:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我见过最棒的超英秘密道具墙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest wall
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of superhero secret gadgetry ever
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要玩宇宙射线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna play with the Cosmic Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.77,0:01:53.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去拿海底手套
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get the Aquaglove
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们给我慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种东西不能随便乱玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You cannot play with this stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那昏沉之球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about the Orb of Confusion?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长时间暴露在昏沉之球附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prolonged exposure to the Orb of Confusion
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.70,0:02:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会导致你们昏昏沉沉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will give you confusion
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那无影船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about the Invisible Boatmobile?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.70,0:02:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无影船最不能乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially not the Invisible Boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们说  什么都不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When we say, "Don't touch anything"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是要表示  什么都不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we mean, "Don't touch anything"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.48,0:02:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:25.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.62,0:02:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清楚明白  靠谱小跟班企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loud and clear, trusted boy companion
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.02,0:02:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钥匙拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here are the keys
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一周后再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll see you in a week
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up, up and away
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星男孩快来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come, BoyPatrick
