Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  他怎么不来追我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, how come he's not chasing us?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他貌似被冻住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's frozen or something
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冻冻冻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fr-fr-fr
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.14,0:03:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冻冻冻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fro-fro-fro
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计是某种牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It appears to be some sort of prison chamber
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.62,0:03:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是用冷冻塔塔酱做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,made out of frozen tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is incredible
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡第一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next to the Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.32,0:03:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔是美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the evil Man Ray is the all-time greatest arch-nemesis
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二大死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有好多问题想问他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have so many questions to ask him
