Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:33.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1026,824)}解冻
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们什么都不能乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not supposed to touch anything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你说你有问题要问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you said you had a question
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could get in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他都说了不能乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said not to touch anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:41.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1208,480)}冰冻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:41.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,816)}解冻
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一样也不能乱解冻超级坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that includes unfreezing a supervillain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  射线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually Mr. uh
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶魔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man Ray, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有你头自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,only your head is free
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.28,0:03:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赐予我至高无上的邪恶特权
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the supreme authority of wickedness
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, the evil Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,命令你们释放我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,command you to release me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.51,0:04:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,立刻脱离这座冰冻牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from this frozen prison at once
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. evil Man Ray, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不能那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你很坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because you're evil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思是说  如果我是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean, if I was good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就会放我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you'd let me go?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样的话  我是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in that case, I am good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, really
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, really?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,really, really
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的真的真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, really, really?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对对  差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, already
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是好人  我是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm good, I'm good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不快放我走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则后果自负
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or you'll suffer dire consequences
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1208,480)}冰冻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,816)}解冻
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fools
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好被我消灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be eradicated
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.40,0:04:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可恶的装置是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this infernal contraption?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别装傻了  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb, Man Ray--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该知道这是痒痒腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you know that's the Tickle Belt
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士在第17集就对你用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman used on you in episode number 17
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(804,166)}痒痒腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418,898)}跟第{\fnArial}17{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}集一个样
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱看那集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love that episode
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴着这腰带肯定逃不走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never get out of here wearing this belt
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要一个邪恶计划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need an evil plan
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骗他们两个把腰带摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that will trick them to take it off me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表演课该派上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for those acting lessons to pay off
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还记得美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩那时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember that part when Mermaidman and Barnacle--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.75,0:05:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.67,0:05:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Woe is me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.60,0:05:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当坏蛋这么久会有何感想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what it's like being evil for so long
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.60,0:05:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How I wish to be
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能有几个好英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only some kind heroes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以带我踏入正轨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would show me the path to decency
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以教你当好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could teach you how to be good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就可以放你走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then we'll let you go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.68,0:06:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That would be fantastic
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要假装到底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll fake my way through this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟上中学那会一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like I did in high school
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好入学好人学校了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you ready for your first day at goodness school?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  拿钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, get your wallet out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  好人第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, goodness lesson number one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到有人掉了钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see someone drop their wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.78,0:06:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  钱包扔地上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, drop the wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what would you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你钱包好像掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I do believe you've dropped your wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着不像我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look familiar to me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.28,0:06:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都看到是你掉的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just saw you drop it--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's not mine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is yours
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.16,0:06:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要当个大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to be a good person
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱包还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and return it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把什么还给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Return what to who?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,414)}裤头村身份证\N不是驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,808)}派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick Star?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的身份证
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this is your ID?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.73,0:06:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发现了这张身份证
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found this ID
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放在你钱包里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in this wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and if that's the case
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱包一定就是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this must be your wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来挺有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That makes sense to me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then take it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是我钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not my wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You dim bulb
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱包收好  不然我就扒了你胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take back your wallet or I'll rip your arms off
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好人不会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good people don't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扒下别人的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rip other people's arms off
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.69,0:07:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  好人第二课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, goodness lesson number two
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.90,0:07:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到有人费劲地搬运一个重包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see someone struggling with a heavy package
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, friend
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.02,0:07:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我注意到你在费尽气力搬运那个包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I noticed you were struggling with that package
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like some help?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我能重来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, can I start over?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我注意到你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I noticed you were
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又得重来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to start again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个笨手笨脚的粉东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You butter-fingered pink thing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,箱子里的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in that box, anyhow?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.92,0:07:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一大堆的钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wallets
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  挠他痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob, tickle him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That tickles
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.00,0:07:54.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过值得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:54.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's worth it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.79,0:08:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  好人第三课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, goodness lesson number three
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在想一个1到100之间的数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of a number between one and 100
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.77,0:08:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个数是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,62
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,62
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.20,0:08:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当好人跟猜数没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's not about being good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放手  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go of it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  只有他做坏事了才能用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, we can use it only when he's bad
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you let go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,频率上升
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Frequency rising
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腰带失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,belt out of control
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连DNA都痒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tickling my DNA
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快停下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it stop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.57,0:08:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他刚才说了请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said the "p" word
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peanuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, "please"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good enough for me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他应该重组了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess he's reconstituted
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫改过自新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rehabilitated
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(776,920)}康       复
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就祝你健康
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gesundheit
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天你毕业了  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's graduation day, Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是通往你未来的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the key to your future
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at him, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大好人的典范
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the picture of goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可以动那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not supposed to touch that stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个也不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not supposed to touch that, either
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的不能乱动那些东西  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are really not supposed to touch those, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好人用不上武器  就比如
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good people have no use for weapons such as
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.17,0:09:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我唯一好的专长  就是作恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing I'm good at is being evil
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, suckers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么味道  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that smell, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是失败的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the smell of defeat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我还以为是我皮肤的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, I thought it was my skin
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管你皮肤了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget about your skin, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔还是坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man Ray is still bad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得有人出手阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and someone has to stop him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.45,0:09:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这项重责大任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a job
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要交给美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the Invisible Boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ignition on
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have a license
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是艘无影船对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is an invisible boat, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就需要无影的驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you need an invisible license
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我最棒的小跟班了  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the best sidekick ever, Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.78,0:10:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地有无影安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness for invisible seat belts
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我让开  傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of my way, fools
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们再也控制不了我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You no longer have control of me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.06,0:10:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这里属于射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now this town belongs to Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别得意得太早  大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, arch villain
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还有昏沉之球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We still have the Orb of Confusion
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不费吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that was easy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606,338)}第一航海银行
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, people
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.55,0:10:44.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:44.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody stand right where you are
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  不准笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, stop giggling
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll have to
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准笑  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing, you fools
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要办什么业务  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what you can do
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me all of your, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.14,0:11:16.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:16.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give me all of your
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腰带没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The belt is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还是觉得痒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I still feel its tickle
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.95,0:11:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做坏事的冲动都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The urge to do bad is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是开个活期存款账户好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just open a checking account
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(612,378)}开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,546)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别怕  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No need to be alarmed, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你教我的好人课让我洗心革面了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your teachings have transformed me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.47,0:11:55.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还开了印着小狗狗的支票
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:55.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have checks with little poodles on them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,470)}射线恶魔
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个我再也用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't be needing this anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  好人朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Farewell, fellow do-gooder
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.38,0:12:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like the real Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们拯救世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We saved the day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是不可思议  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it incredible, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.40,0:12:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你应该知道这个已经关了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you know that thing's turned off, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.38,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(403,389)}松鼠玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:27.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(430,408)}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(320,538)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.27\pos(384,300)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.95\pos(268,336)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.2\pos(534,718)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,414)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(582,740)}喜剧王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  请各位就座
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody settle down
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临喜剧王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Komedy Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家热烈欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, please give a warm welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们第一位喜剧演员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to our first comic
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.62,0:12:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,存在感低的杜奇威廉姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the indiscernible Doogie Williams
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位观众晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接跳过笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to skip the jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.34,0:12:54.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始朝你们扔派
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:54.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get right to the part where I throw pies at you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我表现能跟他一样好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope I do as good as that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  观众看什么都笑得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, those people will laugh at anything
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别紧张  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我帮你暖场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got 'em all warmed up for you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.34,0:13:11.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位鳍声有请海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:11.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your fins together for SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get 'em, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们水母们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.41,0:13:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家先前有注意过盐瓶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have you ever noticed salt shakers?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.91,0:13:24.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  每天晚上打烊都要装满
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:24.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, you fill them up every night at closing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是说  都上哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, I mean, where does it all go?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都明白我意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And tomatoes--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些玩意是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's the deal on those things?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.44,0:13:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为  就是要切成片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because, I mean you chop them up into slices
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.28,0:13:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄到底算蔬菜还是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are they, vegetables or
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fruit?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么就能做番茄酱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what does that make ketchup?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲笑话的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny guy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送你个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a joke for you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西又臭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What smells rotten
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又让人犯困
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and puts people to sleep?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毒气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Noxious gas?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your act
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you ever notice
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叉子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,forks, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叉子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forks?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.32,0:14:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找个幽默的东西讲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make a witty observation
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,PU
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you ever notice
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠的牙齿有多大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how big squirrels' teeth are?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.99,0:14:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全都能在上面停飞机了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you could land a plane on those things
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有松鼠毛是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what's up with that squirrel fur?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来跳蚤也得有家住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess fleas need a home, too
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel fur
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺臭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they smell
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过  大家一样也会臭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but hey, you'd stink, too
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.64,0:15:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,条件是三个月全埋土里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you spent three months buried in dirt
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么必须要不止一只的松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why does it take more than one squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.07,0:15:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能换灯泡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to change a light bulb?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为松鼠傻得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because they're so darn stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太好笑了吧  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a good one, eh, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.31,0:15:23.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:23.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在是出神入化  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was fantastic, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观众全都笑翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really knocked them out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改天再办一次笑话之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll do this joke night again
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就由你来当主演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with you as the headliner
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到我会当上主演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I could be a headliner
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever that is
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主演就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The headliner's the one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以表演过后赚钱加打扫的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who cleans up after the show
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最起码不是让我好自为之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I don't have to clean up my act
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只讲松鼠玩笑就好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stick with the squirrel jokes, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get busy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拖拖拖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mops, mops, mops
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些玩意怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's up with those things?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, really
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.92,0:15:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚的表演你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you like the show?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, a-actually, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.19,0:15:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:15:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些玩笑很伤人  你心里也清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those jokes are hurtful and you know it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么的  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯开个玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just joking
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是说  众所周知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean everybody knows
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是全裤头村最聪明的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're the smartest one at Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我无法反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't argue with that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都会偶尔自嘲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We all gotta laugh at ourselves once in a while
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都自嘲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do it all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.26,0:16:22.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:22.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实有点敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was being a little too sensitive
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别见怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No hard feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,210)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  除臭剂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, deodorant
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买滚珠还是买膏状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roll-on or stick?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她得两个都买
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think she should buy both
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那只笨松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the stupid squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.47,0:16:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起来试着跟它交流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's try and communicate with it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, little critter
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别靠近松鼠  比利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't stand too close to a squirrel, Billy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会被传染傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll catch its stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚蠢不是病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupidity isn't a virus
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但传染力堪比病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it sure is spreading like one
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.83,0:17:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrely, squirrely
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,squirrely, squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为它们就是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because they're stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为它们就是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because they're stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.16,0:17:22.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:22.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些松鼠玩笑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about them squirrel jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就谈过了  记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We already talked about that, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  事情很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, this is serious
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一直给大家开松鼠玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since you've been telling them jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在大家都区别对待我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,people have been treating me different
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  占用五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, five minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hel-lo, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.67,0:17:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.02,0:17:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你明不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you un-der-stand?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrels
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y-y-you see?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我想跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.46,0:17:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:17:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处卖傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's fooling around
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身为你朋友  我要你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking you as a friend
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再讲松鼠玩笑了  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please lay off them squirrel jokes, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向台下观众讲点别的玩笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell some of them other jokes you got
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别的玩笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Other jokes?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a million of them
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你果然还是能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd understand
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.78,0:18:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.18,0:18:24.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位鳍声有请海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your fins together for SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.88,0:18:28.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:28.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.45,0:18:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听过破产金鱼的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about the goldfish who went bankrupt?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在金鱼变铜鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now he's a bronze fish
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.33,0:18:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家应该都听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you heard that one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.87,0:18:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好笑的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  你真是心善
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, you're too kind
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这水怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about this water?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  这玩意到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, the stuff's everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再讲个松鼠跟灯泡的笑话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell the one about the squirrel and the light bulbs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about this thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再讲点松鼠玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get on with the squirrel jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.75,0:19:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你要做出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you've got a choice to make
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选朋友  还是选事业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your friends or your career?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么必须要不止一只的松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How come it takes more than one squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能装灯泡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to screw in a light bulb?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为松鼠就是傻得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because they're so darn stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My people
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.42,0:19:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说真的  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seriously, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特别想感谢我的朋友  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to give a special thanks to my friend Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, don't you see?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观众很爱我开的那些玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The crowd loves these jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们说对不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来吗  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you see, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是在跟你欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're laughing with you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是对你嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not at you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能理解我了不  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很理解现在的情况  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand exactly what's going on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你迟早会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew sooner or later you'd understand
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是宽宏大量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a great sport
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起为珊迪鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's give a big hand to Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.96,0:20:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过鼓掌鼓慢点  因为可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But clap slow, because remember
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她是只松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she's a squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.10,0:20:18.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:18.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都是好观众  然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've been a wonderful audience and, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,good night
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一场精彩的表演  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another spectacular performance, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么  粉丝来信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this, a fan letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:35.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(240,920)}你说的对\N海绵宝宝\N玩笑真好笑\N明天来树屋\N好好庆祝庆祝\N\N珊迪
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.97,0:20:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既保住了事业  又保住了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get to keep your career and your friends
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.00,0:20:46.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:46.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.56,0:20:48.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪总算能看到我的喜剧才能了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:48.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy can finally see the genius of my comedy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.52,0:20:58.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:58.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how-dee
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.08,0:21:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在发扬我的松鼠天性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just being my au-naturally squirrely self
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all must be tired
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给大家讲了好多笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from telling them funny jokes all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.72,0:21:17.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你就休息一下好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:17.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a load off?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.60,0:21:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  这座椅好像有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I think something's wrong with this seat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.56,0:21:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有  我只是涂了点胶水上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Naw, I just done put glue on it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1240,820)}胶水
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样你才不会摔下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you wouldn't fall off
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.13,0:21:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些花是送我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are them flowers for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然还带了个花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You even done got me a vase
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是珊迪  那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Sandy, that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's not a
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太飘亮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't that purdy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我需要水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I need wa
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.04,0:21:39.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:39.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是海底生物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You's a sea critter
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底生物需要什么东西来着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what was that thing sea critters need?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.77,0:21:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底生物需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sea critters need, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wa
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.88,0:21:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know this one
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wa
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.79,0:21:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wallet?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.37,0:21:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.78,0:21:59.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,华夫饼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:21:59.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waffles?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.07,0:22:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.41,0:22:04.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不早点说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:04.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why didn't you just say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.70,0:22:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我们松鼠确实傻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, us squirrels sure is stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.27,0:22:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.57,0:22:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠就是笨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrels is dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.43,0:22:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了珊迪  我都理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sandy, I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.45,0:22:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.69,0:22:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want more?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.84,0:22:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okey-dokey
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.63,0:22:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给海底生物多来点水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More water for the sea critter
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.17,0:22:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.25,0:22:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.67,0:22:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不开松鼠玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more squirrel jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.95,0:22:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.93,0:22:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  非常谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you very much
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.61,0:22:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来的路上撞见了一只松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On my way over here I ran into a squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就说  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I said, "Hey
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.12,0:22:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不找几个松鼠朋友过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"why don't you go get a couple squirrel friends
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起去换个灯泡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we'll go change a light bulb?"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.82,0:22:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过说真的  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But seriously, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.10,0:22:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唯一会比松鼠还傻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the only thing dumber than a squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.00,0:22:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们海绵傻到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're so dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连脊椎都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we don't even have a vertebrae
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.92,0:23:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.22,0:23:07.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:07.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got no bones
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.12,0:23:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.57,0:23:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.27,0:23:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.45,0:23:17.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小气到都不愿意花费注意力了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:17.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're so cheap they can't even pay attention
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.25,0:23:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.40,0:23:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很小气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am cheap
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.52,0:23:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来说说鱼的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let me tell you about those fish
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.70,0:23:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在是臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, are they smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.90,0:23:27.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会有生物
