Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么是肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what is soap?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:41.30,0:23:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更别提海星了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't even get me started on starfish
